transcript: I woke up with my alarm going off and then I got out of bed and took a shower. After that I went into the kitchen and ate a chocolate chip muffin. Then I got into my car, after brushing my teeth, and drove to work. At work I seated people at tables because I am a host, then I checked on the servers to make sure that they were doing okay, then I cleaned the restaurant, made sure that I was completely finished, and then I left to go have lunch with my mother. I had lunch with her at the local Mexican restaurant for about one hour. Then I came home and ate some more food because I was still hungry. And after that I started working on Mechanical Turk where I am still working on this survey right now. That is everything that I've done today so far.
